column2: "Long time no see, boys and girls! Patty's back! Are you doing well? "
"Ah, hello. I'm Tea. It's been a while since we've had this familiar introduction."
"You bet'cha! So much happened! Like that thing... and that other thing..."
"...you don't remember a thing, do you?"
"What's important is all's well that ends well! Ah, doesn't it feel great?"
"<%me>, thank you for all your hard work."
"Well I'm happy to see you again!"
"And get this! After all that, we didn't catch a single break!"
"We're standing on Harkotan, a newly discovered planet! Isn't the contrast of black and white pretty?"
"This isn't the Discovery Channel, Patty. We're here because we discovered a Dark Falz signature."
"The planet is inhabited, but they may not be receptive to us. I do hope our first contact goes well..."
"Who cares! All there is to do is give it everything we've got!"
"...I can't wait to clean up after her. Would it kill Patty to put herself in my shoes?"
